2.Window-dr.SwichToWindow();
3.IFrame-SwitchToIframe();

when we want to access ot automate the element in other windows then we can use Window-dr.SwichToWindow(); function
 for single window we use String parent=dr.getWindowHandle(); method
we use Set<String> wins=dr.getWindowHandles(); to get the window number in multiple windows

for Iframe
dr.switchTo().frame(dr.findElement(By.tagName("iframe")))

